seo: 通达OA, 文件包含漏洞, 漏洞检测, 网络安全
seo_en: Tongda OA, File Inclusion Vulnerability, Vulnerability Detection, Network Security
summary: 该插件用于检测通达OA V2013版本中的文件包含漏洞，通过构造特定请求来验证是否存在高危漏洞风险。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect the file inclusion vulnerability in Tongda OA V2013. It constructs specific requests to verify whether there is a high-risk vulnerability.
